<br>
Yes you fall under Etc.<br>
And with good reason.<br>
<br>
You see Zeit, Cad and the rest left. But they left on good terms. They said their good byes and went their way. Some may have disagreed with their leaving and felt betrayed, but they never spoke poorly about their times in Resolution. In fact they all spoke of it with fond memories.<br>
<br>
Zeit, Cad, Pen will always be my friends regardless of guild tags. And as mad as ppl were I will always be welcome them back.<br>
<br>
