<br>
So yes you thought it best to leave Resolution, try to lower morale, insult people and leave a long post speaking of all the things we did wrong.<br>
<br>
Well Ayrielle, I cannot deny that at times you are a wonderful person. Maybe you just had a bad day that day. However, we've all seen a differnt side of you. The Holier then thou I am perfection and you guys didn't live up attitude.<br>
