I was just the one to take how many people felt and speak my feelings.  Perhaps now others will.  Doesn't matter to me.<br>
<br>
You chose to bring this to the soapbox for all to see.<br>
I left it in a forum where only those who followed Resolution and cared enough to look would read it.  I left it in a place where you could reply. If you had access to the members only section i'd have written my post there, but you didn't and I wanted you to READ what I wrote.<br>
<br>
Remember it was your choice to bring this here to soapbox so FV as a whole could see.  Thats fine with me.  As I said i've never been one to shy away from controversy.   Hell I live for it i'm an Attorney.  So now you concerned many people who contrary to what many of us may think really don't give a fuck about Resolution/FNF or any other Uberguild 001 and are just out to enjoy their EQ lives.  But your ego wouldn't allow that.  <br>
<br>
Thats great, I need to pad my post count here anyway.<br>
<br>
Go get some help ayrielle, learn to distinguish between when RP comments are ok and when even tho you use the guise of RP you are insulting the real people who play this game.<br>
<br>
<br>
Aailin <br>
<br>
ps.  I find it even more amusing that my RP insult to you hit you so hard like a slap in the face.  Just firther proof that somewhere along the way you blurred the line too much and forgot that Real people play this tgame.<br>
